{"id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0005", "text": "多麼想知別人如何能夠", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 9, 3, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["do1", "mo1", "soeng2", "zi1", "bit6", "jan4", "jyu4", "ho4", "nang4", "gau3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "多麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想知", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能夠", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "代表作", "artists": ["關智斌"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2970", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0006", "text": "尋到一生一首曲伴着詞 幸福輕易到手", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 4, 3, 3, 3, 9, 3, 2, 2, 0, 2, 3, 3, 2, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cam4", "dou3", "jat1", "sang1", "jat1", "sau2", "kuk1", "bun6", "zoek6", "ci4", "hang6", "fuk1", "hing1", "ji6", "dou3", "sau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "尋", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一生", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一首", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "曲伴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "詞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幸福", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "輕易", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到手", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "代表作", "artists": ["關智斌"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2970", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0007", "text": "未曾有 沿途上無限次 的分手", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mei6", "cang4", "jau5", "jyun4", "tou4", "mou4", "haan6", "ci3", "dik1", "fan1", "sau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "未曾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沿途", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無限", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "次", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "分手", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "代表作", "artists": ["關智斌"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2970", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0008", "text": "猶如一位演唱太久 毫無得獎歌的歌手", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 3, 2, 9, 4, 4, 9, 0, 0, 3, 9, 3, 3, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jau4", "jyu4", "jat1", "wai6", "jin2", "coeng3", "taai3", "gau2", "hou4", "mou4", "dak1", "zoeng2", "go1", "dik1", "go1", "sau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "猶如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一位", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "演唱", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太久", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "毫無", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得獎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "歌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "歌手", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "代表作", "artists": ["關智斌"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2970", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0009", "text": "時間經已匆匆飛走 卻大志未酬天資不夠", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 5, 3, 3, 3, 9, 4, 2, 4, 2, 0, 3, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["si4", "ging1", "ji5", "cung1", "cung1", "fei1", "zau2", "koek3", "daai6", "zi3", "mei6", "cau4", "tin1", "zi1", "bat1", "gau3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "時間", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "經已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "匆匆", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "飛走", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "卻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "大志", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未酬", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天資", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不夠", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "代表作", "artists": ["關智斌"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2970", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0010", "text": "從來戀歌交到我手 就算多苦心未免最終分手", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 19}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 9, 3, 3, 4, 5, 9, 2, 4, 3, 9, 3, 2, 5, 4, 3, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cung4", "loi4", "lyun2", "go1", "gaau1", "dou3", "ngo5", "sau2", "zau6", "syun3", "do1", "fu2", "sam1", "mei6", "min5", "zeoi3", "zung1", "fan1", "sau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "從來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "戀歌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "交到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就算", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "苦心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未免", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最終", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "分手", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "代表作", "artists": ["關智斌"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2970", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5YWz5pm65paM_Mjk3MA_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
